data.description: Bell Farms Beauty! This over 2000 sqft home has so much to offer! 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a bright and airy open floor plan. The kitchen is open to the living room for a cohesive open living space. This kitchen is amazing, with tons of bright white cabinets and all the counter space you could ever need. The chef in your life will fall in love with the functionality of this space. The living room is perfect for entertaining, the beautiful fireplace is ready for you to enjoy this winter. The master bedroom is HUGE! with an en-suite that makes you feel like your at a spa. It has a separate soaking tub perfect for relaxing.. The large walk-in closet has plenty of space for any amount of clothing. The other three bedrooms are also a great size. The best part is the backyard with an amazing custom pergola and entertaining areas. This home is an entertainers dream and wont last long!
